Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
delete_metric_header(25.10)                        delete_metric_header(25.10)

Name
       delete_metric_header - Deletes the metric header

Syntax
       delete_metric_header

       [-help]

       [-id <database_id>]

       -name <header_name>

       Deletes the metric header.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

              For a detailed description of the command, use the man command:

              man delete_metric_header

       -id <database_id>
              Specifies the database ID

              Data_type: string, optional

       -name <header_name>
              Specifies the header name to be deleted.

              Data_type: string, required

       Example
              * The following command deletes the metric header, User.

                delete_metric_header -name User

Related Information
              * set_metric_header

